---
// Rhodes Ceremony Styles
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:astt3">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-32" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:qp99hc">
    <!-- Beachfront & Pier Ceremonies -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:qp99hd">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:qp99he">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#FDF2F9] text-[#A81E82] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:sskha2">Ceremony Styles</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:v6dzcd">Beachfront & Bay Ceremonies</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:monwc7">
          There's something magical about saying "I do" with the sound of the waves in the background. Rhodes offers spectacular beachfront locations, from St Paul's Bay in Lindos to the long stretches of sand in Faliraki.
        </p>
        <a href="/enquire2" class="inline-block text-[#A81E82] font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b-2 border-[#A81E82] pb-1 hover:text-accent-hover hover:border-accent-hover transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:tslt1c">
          Explore Beach Venues
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7ay">
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7ax">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FDF2F9] rounded-3xl translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7aw"></div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7av">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/33151489/pexels-photo-33151489.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Rhodes Beach Wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:o7055t" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rustic & Traditional -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7au">
      <div class="order-1" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7at">
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7as">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FDF2F9] rounded-3xl -translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7ar"></div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7aq">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/18774893/pexels-photo-18774893.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Rustic Rhodes Wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:o7055u" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-2" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:m1v7ap">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#F5F5F5] text-muted-foreground text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:sskha3">Tradition</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:v6dzcc">Historic & Traditional Charm</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:monwc8">
          Away from the modern resorts, Rhodes is steeped in history. The island offers unique venues like ancient chapels, the magnificent Kalithea Springs, and charming whitewashed village squares for a truly authentic Greek atmosphere.
        </p>
        <a href="/enquire2" class="inline-block text-[#A81E82] font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b-2 border-[#A81E82] pb-1 hover:text-accent-hover hover:border-accent-hover transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/destinations/rhodes/RhodesStyles.astro:tslt1d">
          Explore Historic Venues
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>